Code: EXEC SQL SELECT IMP_SEGURADA_IX, PRM_TARIFARIO_IX, COD_OPCAO, VLPRMTOT, PCIOCC FROM seguros.v1bilhete_cober WHERE COD_EMPRESA IN (0,9999) AND CODPRODU = :CODPRODU AND MODALIFR = :MODALIFR AND VLPRMTOT = :VLPRMTOT AND DTTERVIG BETWEEN '9000-12-31' AND '9999-12-31' AND IDE_COBERTURA = '1' END SQL
